# Import & enrichment

- Import job state and destination publication state are separate in admin reporting.
- `review_queue_items.job_id` → `city_admin_import_jobs.id` only.
- `ImportBatch.id` → `import_batch_id` in payload, never in `job_id` FK.
- Invalid job id → `ReviewQueueJobLinkError` before DB FK crash.
- Discovery bulk-create must not queue import unless `queue_import=true` explicit.
- One canonical taxonomy; idempotent imports; explicit publication flags.
- Collect-max → normalize/dedup → enrich → classify → publish/report.

## Key files

`data/scripts/import_city_osm.py` · `services/import_pipeline/runner.py` · `services/review_queue_service.py`
